data.Interactability_Reward_3_Text: Hey! You there! I know this seems odd but let me explain...
data.Interactability_Reward_4_Text: My name is Anthe Grim! If you've got anything to say, know I can't hear you because I'm... dead.
data.Interactability_Reward_5_Text: You can hear me though! And that's what's important. I think that's now it works?
data.Interactability_Reward_6_Text: I... hope so atleast I don't...
data.Interactability_Reward_7_Text: Anyway! I'm trapped in this magical death crystal thing! Atleast that's what I'd call it... I'd...
data.Interactability_Reward_8_Text: Sorry if it's not obvious, I don't get too many visitors. Thing is, I really need your help.
data.Interactability_Reward_9_Text: You're in what I refer to as the Apparition Plane.
data.Interactability_Reward_10_Text: I’ve been trapped here for who knows how long, and I’m hoping that you can maybe... help free me?
data.Interactability_Reward_11_Text: Right now, it’s just my soul that’s trapped, but you can free me by collecting a few other corrupted souls that will...
data.Interactability_Reward_12_Text: Okay well this whole thing is difficult to explain. You’ll kinda just have to see it.
data.Interactability_Reward_13_Text: Just take this key and find another portal to this world through the real lighthouse on the island.
